title: Jaye Wells-Silver-Tongued Devil
description: Heralded author Jaye Wells has staked out a treasured place on readers' shelves with her breathtaking tales of urban fantasy. Silver-Tongued Devil features Wells' popular creation, heroine Sabina Kane-outcast, assassin, magnet to supernatural species. When a string of murders threatens to stall negotiations between the mages and vampires, Sabina leaps into the fray. But the more she learns, the more she realizes that there are dark forces stirring. And the killer in her sights might be more than capable of shutting her down-for good
